ion of how existing perturbative results at the standard\nscale variation points can be converted to 68%/95% credibility intervals in the\nBayesian approach using the new public code MiHO.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Jun 2021 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Sep 2021 06:58:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-30"}
