ing on the fabrication and\ndesign optimizations, it is possible to achieve throughputs $\\sim 60\\%$ using\nthe SiN platform. Thus, we show that SiN MPW offerings are highly promising and\nwill play a key role in integrated photonic spectrograph developments for\nastronomy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Jun 2021 18:00:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-10"}
