dence of the fluorescence efficiencies can provide a meaningful\ntest of the physical process responsible for the Fe I and Ni I emission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Jun 2021 21:32:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Oct 2021 16:39:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-13"}
