 hydrogen\nreionization completes. Furthermore, our measurements provide a consistency\ncheck on IGM models that explain the Lyman-alpha forest, with the cross\ncorrelation being immune to systematics that are uncorrelated between the two\nforests, such as metal line contamination.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Jun 2021 06:49:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 Oct 2021 00:37:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-27"}
