kein module of the complement of the trefoil, $KBSM(Tr^c)$,\nand we study the effect of braid band moves on elements in the basis of\n$KBSM(Tr^c)$. These moves reflect isotopy in $M$ and are similar to the second\nKirby moves.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Jun 2021 10:21:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-10"}
