ifferent driving conditions, which create new opportunities for\nautonomous vehicles, intelligent tires, and tire slip ratio estimation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Jun 2021 01:41:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 31 Jul 2021 02:25:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 22 Jan 2022 10:06:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-25"}
